							</div>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-color text-2xl shrink-0 mt-1">check_circle</span>
							<div>
								<strong class="text-primary-color">Projetos de incorporação:</strong>
